snippet.title: Chaos Break (PS1) Trailer
snippet.description: Chaos Break (EON Digital Entertainment) was released in the PAL regions in 2000.  It never made its way to America.  It is a fun, action-oriented game with a horror-themed story.  You can play either as Rick or Mitsuki.
